<body>
  <%- include("./partials/nav") %>

  <main class="faq container">
    <div class="page-back-nav">
      <a href="/" class="page-back-link"><i class="bi bi-arrow-left"></i> Back to Dashboard</a>
    </div>

    <section class="faq__hero">
      <p class="faq__eyebrow">FAQ</p>
      <h1 class="faq__title">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
      <p class="faq__subtitle">Quick answers about links, QR codes, plans, analytics, and account flow.</p>
      <p class="faq__ist-clock" data-ist-clock>IST: --</p>
    </section>

    <section class="faq__panel page-panel">
      <div class="faq__content">
        <p class="faq__intro"><strong>Need help using Zipply?</strong> These are the most common questions based on the current product flow.</p>

        <h2>1. Is Zipply free to use?</h2>
        <p>Yes. The Normal plan is free and includes 3 short URLs and 2 QR codes per day.</p>

        <h2>2. What are the paid plan limits?</h2>
        <p>Pro allows 10 short URLs and 10 QR codes per day. Plus allows 25 short URLs and 25 QR codes per day.</p>

        <h2>3. When do daily limits reset?</h2>
        <p>Daily usage limits reset at midnight IST (Asia/Kolkata).</p>

        <h2>4. Do I need an account?</h2>
        <p>Yes. Signup and email OTP verification are required to create and manage links and QR codes.</p>

        <h2>5. Can I set expiry on short links?</h2>
        <p>Yes. You can set an expiry date while creating a short URL. Expired links stop redirecting.</p>

        <h2>6. Can I track clicks and history?</h2>
        <p>Yes. Zipply provides click counts and history details in your dashboard for each short link.</p>

        <h2>7. Can I use custom short IDs?</h2>
        <p>Yes. You can choose your own short ID if it is available and valid.</p>

        <h2>8. What happens if I delete a link or QR?</h2>
        <p>Deleted items are removed from your dashboard history and cannot be recovered.</p>

        <h2>9. Which payment gateway is used?</h2>
        <p>Plan upgrades are processed through Razorpay.</p>

        <h2>10. How can I contact support?</h2>
        <p>For help, visit <a href="/support">Support</a> or email <a href="mailto:amanshow9800@gmail.com">amanshow9800@gmail.com</a>.</p>

        <p class="faq__footer"><strong>Last updated:</strong> April 2026.</p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <%- include("./partials/footer") %>
